title: Couple With Heart Man Man Dark Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone

On Apple devices, the figures are drawn with Apple's signature soft rounded edges and subtle 3D shading, conveying intimacy and affection. The vibrant heart, filled with rich color and realistic highlights, symbolizes deep love, partnership, and connection between two men.
